1. PRODUCT INFO :

Spray-in texturizer creates sexy, tousled, windswept hairstyles

2. FOR WHOM / USE :

Designed to enhance a natural, wavy look and piecey separation, this spray-in texturizer nourishes hair while creating a soft, touchable texture. Sea minerals and nourishing ocean botanicals keep hair soft and healthy.

3. FOR WHAT / BENEFITS :

● Provides natural waves & separation

● Nourishing ocean botanicals provide a “fresh from the beach” look 

● Fortifying Sea Minerals give hair light, tossable texture

● Control: 5 of 10

● Formulated without sulfates, gluten, sodium chloride or parabens

4. ABOUT THE COLLECTION :

L’ANZA Healing Style is the only line of styling products that heals the hair while creating versatile and fashionable looks. These formulations provide utmost protection from damaging heat and UV rays while maintaining healthy, manageable hair. Advanced technology and botanical styling ingredients provide long-lasting hold without cracking, flaking or residue. Healthy hair is always in style.
